Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:19.08,box,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:24.96,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:26.79,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.00,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:31.71,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:40.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:41.96,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:46.27,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.55,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.80,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:53.44,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Still asleep, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.70,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:59.07,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You were up late \Npacking for the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:00.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Move?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:03.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:07.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was with Noel at the \Nobservatory until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:08.16,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:09.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You know her, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.71,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You helped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.36,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:17.64,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you can see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:23.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:09.96,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(860,271)}Saucerless City
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:12.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.91,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.41,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired from the \Nlong trip from Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is it summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.01,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:27.24,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It was snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.89,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean in your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:36.73,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably get \Nsome rest once we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.83,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:45.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.69,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:50.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come home later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:51.79,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Later?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.17,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you remember where we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.17,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do!
