Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.15,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.33,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sightseeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.58,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.66,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We were just at the \Nobservatory until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.68,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,The observatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.59,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You do remember me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.32,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.73,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.71,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:55.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Since we were kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:05:00.19,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You left the city \Nwithout saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.69,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We were all so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.95,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about \Nseven years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.03,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been that long, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.58,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.91,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It was winter until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:17.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But Noel disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.29,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,and the saucer disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.56,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.09,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:28.47,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't know what \Nyou're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:31.07,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm glad to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What about Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.43,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.69,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:51.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:03.42,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.82,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.40,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka? {\i1}That{\i0} Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.46,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.13,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,How nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:25.65,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We all used to go to \Nthe observatory to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.09,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember, Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.61,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What we did in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.95,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We called a saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:39.40,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We held hands in a circle, \Nand we made wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.67,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there's no \Nway a saucer would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.96,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.82,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.66,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.47,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you ever thought about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:07:00.79,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What if a saucer really \Nshowed up that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.01,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.85,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how did you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.26,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:19.00,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.68,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:24.07,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We played at the observatory \Nwhen we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:26.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.68,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty well-built, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:44.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Let's go launch it at the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:49.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We've launched it together once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:53.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,When we were kids, \Nwe gathered at the observatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,and called the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:59.34,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,A saucer actually showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.35,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,A saucer came to the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.51,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember you \Nmaking jokes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.34,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:19.85,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember even just a little \Nabout the saucer? About Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.85,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:25.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please, remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.86,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Souta, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.67,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.41,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's exchange contact info.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:43.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yuzuki. I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.37,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,To see Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shione is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:30.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:31.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:34.76,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.44,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is there a Togawa Shione here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:44.77,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, there's no one by \Nthat name living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.67,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:54.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:04.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't anyone \Nknow about the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.17,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko. Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.36,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:34.22,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I remember Noel, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.47,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:54.56,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.37,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I moved all our boxes inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.11,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a lot of cleaning \Nup to do tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is the saucer gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:27.82,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Or did it never come to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:39.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just let this be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Back there, Noel was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.03,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Two eggs, yolks still runny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.09,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.55,sora-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Our next story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:27.37,sora-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,A new hotspot has shown \Nup in Hokubi City.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.55,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.91,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:52.99,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.93,Observatory,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Maeyama \NObservatory
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.86,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Komiya Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:11.55,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:12.76,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:17.60,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Komiya-san moved here from \NTokyo because of her father's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:20.21,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, be good to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:24.59,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Komiya-san, your seat is in the \Nfar back of the second row.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.56,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:41.26,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad we weren't \Nin the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:44.94,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Now that Nonoka's back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.72,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we go hang out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:50.03,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I want to talk to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.03,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,About the observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.39,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to call \NSouta, too, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.34,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We want to know what \Nyou've been up to, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.58,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.92,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know which class she's in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.60,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Not in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.06,sora-main-top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:14.72,sora-main-top,,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, you're free right now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.93,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She moved away during \Nelementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:21.10,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shione's always wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.89,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have her contact info?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.94,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.94,sora-main-top,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:27.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.45,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:41.31,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The five of us did try to call \Na saucer when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You might not recall now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,but in the city I know, \Nthere was a saucer above the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,and a girl named Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:53.59,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying we've forgotten about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:56.60,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You've all seen the city \Nwith the saucer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:16:00.46,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're an important part of \Nour time at the observatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.91,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,and you're a precious \Nfriend to us now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.72,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.36,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:12.49,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought it'd be \Nnice if a saucer came down
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:16.37,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,and granted our wishes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.87,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:22.79,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.60,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Something about Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Something about the \Ntime we spent with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Her words, her expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember something, \Neven just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:34.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:38.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise Noel will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.02,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be so harsh,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.08,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe you're just imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.28,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one that remembers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:55.47,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,this Noel, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:16:59.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.62,sora-flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean in your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.62,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:09.04,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel worked really hard \Nto grant our wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, and yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You've all seen her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:19.30,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't think there's any \Npoint talking about this any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:25.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Souta, you don't \Nhave to say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Souta's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.91,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.25,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.32,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.48,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Does Noel really exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:25.95,Keep Out,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:34.50,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm the only one \Nthat remembers Noel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,then if I forget Noel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,she'll really disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:51.07,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to record everything \NI know about Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:55.56,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It should go further.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:04.01,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What am I missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.12,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:26.36,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:33.81,Shiihara,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shiihara Market
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.48,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've been watching \Nover this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.86,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You'd know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:45.70,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Something important \Nthat I might have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:48.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:05.60,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, I miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.19,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Smile again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Could that even happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:33.00,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Could it really all \Nhave been a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Could Noel really not exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Could it really be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:43.76,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Could it really be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.29,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:02.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seven years, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:07.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when \Nwe were kids here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.91,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:16.67,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What I remember are that girl's tears \Non the night of the meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:35.66,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:39.56,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Noel didn't like seeing you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:44.56,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.50,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
